{"word":"ἀπροβούλευτος","slug":"ἀπροβούλευτος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀπροβούλευτος</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:προβουλεύω'><el>προβουλεύω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>not planned beforehand, unpremeditated</i>, <b><a href='S:Aristotle'>Arist.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>not submitted to the</i> <el>βουλή</el>, <b><a href='S:Demosthenes'>Dem.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><a href='S:active signification'><a href='S:Active voice'>act.</a></a> <i>without forethought</i>, <b><a href='S:Aristotle'>Arist.</a></b>:—<a href='S:Adverb'>adv.</a> <el>-τως</el>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}